{"tid":1208049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教協認為現時社會氣氛急劇惡化　發動本周全港罷課","createTime":"2019-06-12T08:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T09:00:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":100,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5db9205bdfbe00840998d7be65e37a1421561cf","tid":1208049,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"教協宣布發動本周全港罷課。<br />\n<br />\n教協發聲明說，政府不惜一切硬推惡法，立法會主席梁君彥不斷加開會議配合政府，做法必須譴責。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，現時有大批市民於金鐘一帶聚集，教協強烈要求警方克制，並強調警方使用過分武力，將令市民和政府的關係推進深淵。<br />\n<br />\n教協認為，現時社會氣氛正急劇惡化，決定宣布發動本周全港罷課，呼籲大專院校仍有課堂的教師配合罷課，並提供日後補課安排；又呼籲中學教師與校方商討，訂出罷課具體安排；小學教師回校罷教，在課堂上向學生解釋事件；而幼稚園及幼兒園教師則要緊守崗位，照顧年幼學童。<br />\n<br />\n教協呼籲校方理解罷課罷教是重要決定，希望支持校長和教師的選擇。家長可以自行決定是否讓子女回校。"},{"pid":"fe25649315a58ec65aff83763d2fd4826e199414","tid":1208049,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7efe1b9c8b321f58e78f83e50bfe4bda4446908","tid":1208049,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:46:28.000Z","msg":"蔡若蓮呢"},{"pid":"c3f76f8658ef7e0bc40acaa325c2bfb538dd916f","tid":1208049,"uid":149316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c038962d7396bd160159c2763b2ae6840046b2f","tid":1208049,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:49:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cd4e14a24f4d51f019be1b4b7ab1801975bbcf9","tid":1208049,"uid":118949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0